Surveys:
——————————————————————————————————————————
https://trailhead.salesforce.com/content/learn/modules/survey-basics?trailmix_creator_id=strailhead&trailmix_slug=prepare-for-your-salesforce-business-analyst-credential

Setup search: Feature Settings -> survey -> survey settings

must first enable surveys to use them. Once enabled, you can find surveys in the app launcher
	app launcher -> surveys

Once your survey is complete, you can click preview so you can preview how an end user would view the survey
——————————————————————————————————————————
To open a survey, you have to click the arrow button on the right and click 'open latest version'
	if you simply click the name, it will only take you to the survey components

To send your survey out, open the latest version and instead of being in the 'view' tab, you can select the 'send' tab

Once you get your results, you can analyze the results of your survey by selecting the 'analyze' tab next to the 'view' and 'send' tabs.
You can export the results in an excel format by sending it to yourself
——————————————————————————————————————————
Good questions are open ended questions 
	-ask how and why